graph TD
    A[Donor Signs Up] --> B{Donor Type?}
    B -->|Individual Donor| C[Fill Personal Information]
    B -->|Corporate Donor| D[Fill Corporate Information]
    C --> E[Account Created]
    D --> E
    E --> F{Next Action?}
    F -->|Create Own NGO| G[Register NGO on Platform]
    F -->|Interact with Existing NGOs| H[Browse Available NGOs]
    G --> I[NGO Profile Setup Complete]
    I --> J[Access Donor Dashboard]
    H --> J

    J --> K[Create New Brief/Project]
    K --> L[Fill Brief Details]
    L --> M{Set Visibility?}
    M -->|Private| N[Select Specific NGOs]
    M -->|Public| O[Available to All NGOs]
    M -->|Selected Area| P[Target Specific Geographic Area]
    N --> Q{Save or Push?}
    O --> Q
    P --> Q

    Q -->|Save as Draft| R[Brief Saved - Draft State]
    Q -->|Push to Active| S{Check Wallet Balance}

    R --> T{Ready to Publish?}
    T -->|Yes| S
    T -->|No| U[Edit Draft Later]
    U --> R

    S -->|Sufficient Funds| V[Brief Activated - Notifications Sent]
    S -->|Insufficient Funds| W[Redirect to Wallet Funding]
    W --> X{Funding Method?}
    X -->|International Payment| Y[Use Stripe]
    X -->|Local Payment| Z[Use Paystack]
    Y --> AA[Wallet Funded]
    Z --> AA
    AA --> V

    V --> AB[Create Project Milestones]
    AB --> AC[Define Milestone Details]
    AC --> AD[Set Milestone Targets & Deadlines]
    AD --> AE[Milestones Published]

    AE --> AF[NGOs Receive Notifications]
    AF --> AG[Monitor NGO Applications]
    AG --> AH{Review Applications}
    AH -->|Message for Details| AHM[Open Messaging<br/>with NGO]
    AHM --> AHO[Ask Questions<br/>About Proposal]
    AHO --> AHP{Continue Review?}
    AHP -->|Yes| AH
    AHP -->|No| AIR{Make Decision}

    AH -->|Approve| AI[Select NGO Partner]
    AH -->|Reject| AJ[Notify NGO - Application Rejected]
    AIR -->|Approved| AI
    AIR -->|Rejected| AJ

    AJ --> AJM{Message NGO?}
    AJM -->|Yes| AJN[Send Message<br/>Explaining Decision]
    AJN --> AJO[Discuss Feedback]
    AJO --> AG
    AJM -->|No| AG

    AI --> AIM{Message NGO?}
    AIM -->|Yes| AIMN[Open Messaging<br/>with NGO]
    AIMN --> AIMO[Discuss Project Start<br/>Expectations & Timeline]
    AIMO --> AIK[Release 30percent Budget for Mobilization]
    AIM -->|No| AIK

    AIK --> AL[Project Officially Started]
    AL --> AM[Monitor Milestone Updates<br/>from NGO]

    AM --> AMR[NGO Submits Milestone<br/>Update]
    AMR --> AMR2[Donor Receives:<br/>Documentation & Evidence]
    AMR2 --> AMR3[Review Description &<br/>Progress Metrics]
    AMR3 --> AMP{Verify Milestone<br/>Completion}

    AMP -->|APPROVED ✅| AMQ[Milestone Verified<br/>& Approved]
    AMQ --> AMQP[💰 Release Payment<br/>to NGO Wallet]
    AMQP --> AMQM{More Milestones?}
    AMQM -->|Yes| AMQN[Continue Monitoring<br/>Next Milestone]
    AMQN --> AM
    AMQM -->|No| APF["📋 All Milestones<br/>Submitted"]

    AMP -->|REJECTED ❌| AMREJ[Milestone Rejected]
    AMREJ --> AMREJ2[Project Terminated<br/>No Further Payment]
    AMREJ2 --> AMREJ3[End]

    AMP -->|NEEDS REVISION 🔄| AMM[Request Changes<br/>from NGO]
    AMM --> AMH{Message NGO<br/>for Clarification?}
    AMH -->|Yes| AMHM[Open Messaging<br/>with NGO]
    AMHM --> AMHO[Explain Required<br/>Revisions & Issues]
    AMHO --> AMH2{Need to<br/>Discuss More?}
    AMH2 -->|Yes| AMHM
    AMH2 -->|No| AM
    AMH -->|No| AM

    APF --> APD{Mark Project<br/>as COMPLETED?}
    APD -->|Yes| APDC[Mark as COMPLETED]
    APD -->|No| APD2[Request Additional<br/>Work/Milestones]
    APD2 --> AM
    
    APDC --> AQL[Generate Final<br/>Project Report]
    AQL --> AQS[View Project Report<br/>& Impact Summary]
    AQS --> AS[Project Officially<br/>Marked COMPLETED]
    AS --> AT[End]

    style A fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style E fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style V fill:#2196F3,color:#fff
    style AL fill:#2196F3,color:#fff
    style AS fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style AT fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style AHM fill:#9C27B0,color:#fff
    style AJN fill:#9C27B0,color:#fff
    style AIMN fill:#9C27B0,color:#fff
    style AMHM fill:#9C27B0,color:#fff
    style AMQP fill:#FF5722,color:#fff
    style AMQ fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style APDC fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style AMREJ fill:#f44336,color:#fff
